title: Picnic Time's Pioneer 346-76
transcripts: The Pioneer basket by Picnic Time was inspired by the covered wagons of the early frontier settlers lightweight and durable is an original Picnic Time design the features a wooden frame covered in canvas and a leatherette wrapped handle for comfort the Pioneer is equipped with a handy stylish double lid, two front pockets and a reinforced water-resistant base. This unique basket includes all the amenities required for a deluxe picnic for two including two 8 inch porcelain plates, Two hand blown wine glasses, two stainless steel knives, forks, and spoons a set of salt and pepper shakers, two cotton napkins, stainless steel way to style corkscrew six-inch hard wood cutting board, a stainless steel cheese knife with wooden handle, a quilted blanket, and a plastic food storage container available in 2 elegant color schemes the Pioneers not only ideal for a picnic but also great for any gift giving occasion.
